---

<section id="why-us" class="relative py-24 px-6 bg-black border-t border-gray-800/50 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Animated gradient background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-950/20 via-black to-purple-950/20"></div>
  
  <!-- Grid overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-5"></div>
  
  <!-- Glowing orbs -->
  <div class="absolute top-20 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-indigo-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  
  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <!-- Section badge -->
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 mb-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500/10 to-purple-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-indigo-300">Our Difference</span>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-indigo-200 to-purple-200 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Why Choose CyberBros
        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">We're not your typical web-focused security trainers—we specialize where others don't</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="relative group bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-900/40 to-purple-900/40 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-indigo-500/50 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-indigo-400/70 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-indigo-500/30">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500/10 to-transparent rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        <div class="relative flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600/50 to-purple-600/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-indigo-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-200 mb-3">Niche Expertise That's Rare</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-200 mb-3">Most trainers focus only on web apps. We specialize in:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
              <li>✓ <span class="text-white font-semibold">Thick client security</span> (Windows, .NET, legacy apps)</li>
              <li>✓ <span class="text-white font-semibold">Embedded & IoT security</span> (hardware, firmware)</li>
              <li>✓ <span class="text-white font-semibold">Mobile app security</span> (Android/iOS deep-dive)</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-indigo-300 text-sm mt-3 font-bold">These skills are in HIGH demand but SHORT supply</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative group bg-gradient-to-br from-green-900/40 to-emerald-900/40 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-green-500/50 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-green-400/70 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-green-500/30">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500/10 to-transparent rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        <div class="relative flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-600/50 to-emerald-600/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-green-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-200 mb-3">Filter Bugs Before Expensive Pentests</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-200 mb-3">Our approach for organizations:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
              <li>✓ Train your team to catch <span class="text-white font-semibold">70% of bugs in-house</span></li>
              <li>✓ Reduce pentest costs by <span class="text-white font-semibold">60-80%</span></li>
              <li>✓ Build <span class="text-white font-semibold">permanent internal capability</span></li>
              <li>✓ Handle legacy systems <span class="text-white font-semibold">others won't touch</span></li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-green-300 text-sm mt-3 font-bold">Why pay RM80K for pentests when training costs RM5-15K?</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative group bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900/60 to-gray-950/60 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700/50 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-indigo-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-indigo-500/20">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        <div class="relative flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600/40 to-purple-600/40 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-indigo-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Real-World Practitioners</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Led by active cybersecurity professionals with hands-on experience, not just academic theory. We work on real security assessments and bring current industry knowledge to every session.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative group bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900/60 to-gray-950/60 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700/50 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-purple-500/20">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        <div class="relative flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600/40 to-pink-600/40 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">100% Customized to Your Needs</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Whether you're a student building a portfolio or an SME securing legacy VB.NET apps, we tailor content to your exact situation. No generic, one-size-fits-all training here.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative group bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900/60 to-gray-950/60 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700/50 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-indigo-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-indigo-500/20">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        <div class="relative flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600/40 to-blue-600/40 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-indigo-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Hands-On & Practical</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Every session includes real tools, live demos, and hands-on labs. You'll work with actual vulnerable applications and systems, not just PowerPoint slides.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative group bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900/60 to-gray-950/60 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700/50 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-pink-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-pink-500/20">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        <div class="relative flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-600/40 to-purple-600/40 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-pink-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Flexible & Accessible</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">On-site or remote, weekdays or weekends, short workshops or multi-week programs. Based in KL, serving all of Malaysia with student-friendly and enterprise-ready options.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Key Differentiator Callout -->
    <div class="relative group bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 via-purple-600 to-pink-600 p-10 rounded-3xl text-center border border-indigo-400/50 shadow-2xl shadow-indigo-500/30 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 via-pink-600 to-indigo-600 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
      <div class="relative">
        <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Build Your Security Capabilities</h3>
        <p class="text-indigo-50 text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-6">
          We help you develop long-term security expertise in your team, specializing in areas most trainers avoid.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-black/30 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-2xl max-w-2xl mx-auto border border-white/10">
          <p class="text-white font-bold text-2xl mb-4">What You Gain:</p>
          <ul class="text-left text-indigo-100 space-y-3 text-lg">
            <li>✓ <span class="font-bold text-white">Cost Effective:</span> Training investment vs repeated consulting costs</li>
            <li>✓ <span class="font-bold text-white">Lasting Value:</span> Build permanent internal capability</li>
            <li>✓ <span class="font-bold text-white">Better Quality:</span> Catch issues early in development</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p class="text-indigo-100 mt-6">
          We specialize in thick clients, embedded systems, and mobile apps—niche areas requiring deep expertise.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .bg-grid-pattern {
    background-image: 
      linear-gradient(to right, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
  }
</style>
